item.description:

    [/quote]

not kwl…i find it horrible no offence

Wtf was the reason for this post and its a gun thats not even able to be equipped…

Its probably drawn in paint because thats all your work is, You cant even flip an image correctly for your client and you used as the background anyway…

You guys are retarded, she made a simple model, but she made it in the right format so it can be used with RSMV, that means she done what only like 3 people have done.

So sdfu, and flaming her client, sure, it has glitches etc, but you try making one, compressing all the models so they can be read as a new cache and keeping the same item id’s when runescape’s items id’s are different, so the information etc will be all wrong.

And by the way, she was the first person to find out how to add new sprites, so you would still be on 317 game frame.
She was the first person to add NEW items, not recoloured, me and haxerownsmopar were like 4th but we didn’t create an unpacker and packer to edit the cache.
She was the second/first person to add NEW models, homemade ones, unless ownage plz was first.

She has bought this community loads of stuff, even if some things aren’t helpful for retards such as yourselves, she still is way above you in the moparscape food chain.[/quote]never said her client sucks read first
